Set up your own Blog Like this&hellip; Generally follow this link  Install Hugo on macOS (Homebrew):  Type in console: 
 brew install hugo   Register on Git Create Page  - hugo new site sitename - cd sitename  Select Theme  - git init - cd themes - git submodule add https://github.com/budparr/gohugotheme-ananke.git themes/ananke  Open config.toml in a text editor and add theme = &ldquo;ananke&rdquo;
Local test  hugo server -D
